'''CyberLink''' is a multimedia software company that produces DVD playback, [[digital home]], TV and burning software including [[PowerCinema]] (digital home), [[PowerDirector]] (video editing), DVD Suite (multimedia software suite), [[PowerDVD]], [[PowerProducer]] (DVD authoring) and [[Power2Go]] (burning).Cyberlink also produce MediaShow, [[CyberLink MediaShow]] is a software application for organizing, editing and sharing photos and videos.
Cyberlink's headquarters are based in [[Taipei]], [[Taiwan]] with worldwide offices in [[Fremont, California|Fremont]], [[United States|USA]]; [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]]; and the [[Netherlands]]. The company was founded in 1996.
